OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776175862
OL,3,CStarmer establishes new cabinet
OL,4,Ccommittee to address impact of war in
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister has set up a new
OL,8,Fcabinet committee to deal with the
OL,9,Fimpact of the war in Iran.
OL,11,FSir Keir Starmer will chair the newly-
OL,12,Festablished Middle East Response
OL,13,FCommittee when it meets for the first
OL,14,Ftime on Tuesday to consider the
OL,15,Fsituation in the Strait of Hormuz and
OL,16,Fits impact on global oil and gas
OL,17,Fsupplies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
