PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776175862
OL,3,CStarmer establishes new cabinet
OL,4,Ccommittee to address impact of war in
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FDowning Street sources compared the
OL,8,Fnew panel to the committees set up
OL,9,Funder Tory prime ministers to deal
OL,10,Fwith Brexit preparations and the Covid-
OL,11,F19 pandemic.
OL,13,FITV News understands the committee
OL,14,Fwill focus on medium-term scenario
OL,15,Fplanning to respond to developments in
OL,16,Fthe region over the coming weeks and
OL,17,Fmonths.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776175862
OL,3,CStarmer establishes new cabinet
OL,4,Ccommittee to address impact of war in
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FAlongside the ministerial committee,
OL,8,Fwhose full membership has not yet been
OL,9,Fdisclosed, senior officials will meet
OL,10,Funder the chairmanship of Cabinet
OL,11,FSecretary Dame Antonia Romeo.
OL,13,FThis committee will remain separate
OL,14,Ffrom both regular cabinet meetings and
OL,15,Fthe usual Cobra meetings held to
OL,16,Fdiscuss urgent and important issues
OL,17,Faffecting the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
