OL,3,CStarmer establishes new cabinet
OL,4,Ccommittee to address impact of war in
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe first meeting's focus on the
OL,13,FStrait of Hormuz comes after Donald
OL,14,FTrump announced an American blockade
OL,15,Fof Iranian ports.
OL,17,FThe US president and military
OL,18,Fofficials threatened all ships
OL,19,Fentering or leaving Iranian ports and
OL,20,Fcoastal areas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
