PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776175862
OL,3,CStarmer establishes new cabinet
OL,4,Ccommittee to address impact of war in
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FThey said they would still allow ships
OL,8,Ftravelling between non-Iranian ports
OL,9,Fto transit the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,11,FIran has selectively closed off the
OL,12,Fstrait since the US-Israeli bombing
OL,13,Fcampaign began.
OL,15,FSome tankers have been able to pass
OL,16,Fthrough, but only with the permission
OL,17,Fof the Iranians and a hefty toll.
OL,19,FTrump's blockade is aimed at starving
OL,20,FIran of revenue from those ships.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
