OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776175862
OL,3,CStarmer establishes new cabinet
OL,4,Ccommittee to address impact of war in
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FCriticising the prime minister's focus
OL,8,Fin this first meeting, Tory leader
OL,9,FKemi Badenoch said his priotity should
OL,10,Fbe "defence readiness", linking the
OL,11,Fcrisis to Lord George Robertson's
OL,12,Fcriticism of the government's handling
OL,13,Fof defence preparedness earlier on
OL,14,FTuesday.
OL,16,F"We can't help anyone if we haven't
OL,17,Fgot ships that are fit to sail.
OL,19,F"I was really worried when I saw HMS
OL,20,FDragon taking two weeks to get out of
OL,21,FPortsmouth.
OL,26,@{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
