OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776175862
OL,3,CStarmer establishes new cabinet
OL,4,Ccommittee to address impact of war in
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,F"That is something that Keir Starmer
OL,8,Freally need(s) to think about. I'm
OL,9,Fwilling to work cross party with him,
OL,10,Fbut if he doesn't have a defence plan,
OL,11,Fthen he's just having a meeting to
OL,12,Ftalk about a meeting."
OL,14,FLord George Robertson launched a
OL,15,Fscathing criticism of the government
OL,16,Fearlier on Tuesday in a preview of a
OL,17,Fspeech he was expected to deliver
OL,18,Flater that evening.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@LpmpD@NpntD@VO]
