PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776175862
OL,3,CStarmer establishes new cabinet
OL,4,Ccommittee to address impact of war in
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FStarmer's meeting on Tuesday comes as
OL,8,Finternational leaders prepare to
OL,9,Fgather in Paris on Friday in an effort
OL,10,Fto come up with a plan to ensure the
OL,11,FStrait of Hormuz can remain open to
OL,12,Fshipping after the Middle East war
OL,13,Fends.
OL,15,FThe meeting will be co-hosted by Sir
OL,16,FKeir Starmer and French President
OL,17,FEmmanuel Macron.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
