OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776175862
OL,3,CStarmer establishes new cabinet
OL,4,Ccommittee to address impact of war in
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FA Downing Street spokesman said: "The
OL,8,Fsummit will advance work towards a
OL,9,Fcoordinated, independent,
OL,10,Fmultinational plan to safeguard
OL,11,Finternational shipping once the
OL,12,Fconflict ends."
OL,14,FStarmer told MPs on Monday the UK-
OL,15,FFrench initiative would involve
OL,16,F"military planning to provide
OL,17,Fassurance to shipping" as well as
OL,18,Fdiplomatic efforts.
OL,26,@oD@bOUtD@OO]xD@AOUyD@VO]
