OL,3,CStarmer establishes new cabinet
OL,4,Ccommittee to address impact of war in
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FMacron has previously said the
OL,8,Fcountries participating in the
OL,9,Finitiative would work on a "strictly
OL,10,Fdefensive mission, separate from the
OL,11,Fwarring parties to the conflict",
OL,12,Fwhich "is intended to be deployed as
OL,13,Fsoon as circumstances permit".
OL,15,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,16,Four political experts are across all
OL,17,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,18,Fto the latest episode below...
